subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which 15th-century emperor established the city of Jaipur?
question_hi: जैवन्तगर परमाणु के नाम के वर्षों के दशक, जैवन्तगर का कैसा राजा जिसने जापान के बने थे?
explanation_en: Jai Singh II was the ruler who established Jaipur, the capital of Rajasthan. He built the city in the late 18th century.
